name.k: ニード・フォー・スピード ノーリミットレーシング
Need for Speed No Limits Game

platformAttributes.ios.subtitle.k: 極速狂飆。 稱霸街頭。
車のゲーム、レース、戦いに挑戦してください。街路を支配する

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: A glistening stretch of rain-soaked pavement lies before you. Will you drift, draft or smash your way to victory? Whatever your style, this iconic street racer delivers hugely fun arcade action. Impressive graphics make every Subaru, Porsche and McLaren a sight to behold, and a vast lineup of events gives you plenty of ways to show opponents your taillights. Individual races are enjoyably brief, and we got swept up in blazing through them to unlock the most exotic cars and discover the next challenges.
